
'''Grace Adams''' (wɔwoo no November da a ɛtɔ so 2 , afe 1995) yɛ Ghanani bɔɔlobɔfo a osi akan sɛ atenatofo ma Ghana mmaa bɔɔlobɔkuo a ɛde Berry Ladies ne Ghana man mmaa bɔɔlobɔkuo Ghana women's national team.

== Bɔɔlobɔkuo ==
Adams hyɛɛ bɔɔlobɔ nnwuma ase wɔ Ghana wɔ Ghana Prison Ladies<ref>Police find their target to finish on top (modernghana.com)</ref>, ɛno akyi na otu kɔɔ United states kɔtoaa n'adesua ne osuani agodini agodini. Onyaa akwanya koo suapɔn a ɛde University of South Florida firi afe 2015 kosii afe 2018 mu, na ɔbɔ maa wɔn bɔɔlobɔkuo a ɛde South Florida Bulls wo American Athletics Conference<ref>https://gousfbulls.com/sports/womens-soccer/roster/grace-adams/11357</ref>. Odii nkunim wo afe 2017 ofa no mu.

Wo August da ɛtɔ so 16, afe 2019 mu no, ɔde ne ho kɔ dɔɔm bɔɔlobɔkuo ɛde Rivers Angels a wosi akan wɔ Nigeria Women Premier League a ɛyɛ afe baako kɔntraagye. Wo ɔpepɔn da a ɛtɔ so 24, afe 2020 mu no, Adam de nsa hyehyɛɛ nkrataa ase maa SAAS a ɛwɔ Lebanon, wɔ bre 2019-20 no mfinfin. Osii akan mpen nsɔn na ɔboaa atenato mpɛn 5; ɔboaa n'afa no maa wodii nkunim wɔ saa bɔɔlobɔ afe no mu.

Adam san n'akyi baa Ghana bɛbɔɔ  maa Berry Ladies wɔ National Women's League no mu.

== Amanman mu akansie ==
Adam bɛyɛɛ Sahene maa mmaa wonni mfe 20 a wɔde Under-20 no wɔ 2014 FIFA U-20 Women's World Cup no mu. Wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ dubaako no da a ɛtɔ so 30 no mu no, Adam sii akan maa Ghanaman mmaa mpanyinfoɔ bɔɔlobɔkuo no, wo bre a na adamfofa akansie bi bɔɔ so wɔ wɔn ne Morocco ntam; ɔbaa mu wɔ sima 80 no mu ma Ghana dii nkunim 2-0.

